<p>A stunning space leading to the terrace and jacuzzi for relaxing and luxuriating with a gorgeous view of the Maltese countryside as far as the sea.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/xara-palace/xara-palace-2.jpg" alt="xara-palace-2.jpg" /></p>

<p>The king-size bed, fine linen and beautiful colour schemes are a lovely hideaway from the sunshine when you come in. There is of course a full array of goodies from individually controlled A/C, satellite TV, Wi-Fi, hairdryer and a trouser press to exquisite toiletries from Lâ€™Occitane in the elegant marble bathroom. If you need to re-charge your batteries and enjoy some serene time, then this is the room for you.</p>

