<p>A stunning space with great views and gorgeous bistro menu as well as Afternoon Tea, the inside/outside space is perfect for coffee, breakfast, business meetings, girlsâ€™ lunch, you name it, the Palazzo de Piro is the go-to place in Mdina.</p>

